{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, nobody-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was-- it was not possible to be friends with non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we did everything together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- last-- two years ago, we met again in Mainz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The city invited us-- the Jew-- former Jewish-- former inhabitants of the Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've been doing that for four years now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they invited most of our class, our year, together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must say I pushed them a little on that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- those of us who were still alive were extremely happy to see each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you-- you attended this school and you went to a Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it-- it was-- this school was a school that went all the way through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever, first grade through-- what-- what-- what was in-- in Germany was the-- the last grade, [? prima. ?] And-- and they-- and they-- did-- the-- the-- the exam for that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went from the fifth grade on, till 1938, when the synagogue was first burned and then dynamited.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, there was no-- no going there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and for the rest of my stay in Germany, we were sort of, oh, an empty apartment here, an empty room there, or, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- it was, well, no longer the school that we knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
